---
title: Quick Herby Chicken & Brown Butter Sauce with Potato Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: The garlicky, buttery sauce is the star of this meal, drizzled over tender chicken to add juiciness and flavour. Let’s add a creamy mash to help soak up the last of that sauce, and some steamed veggies to cut through all that richness. Bon appétit!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
